  <evidence rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">How We Use Your Information We may use the information we collect from and about you to contact you from time to time For example we may send you promotional offers materials and other communications and information about Kraft its portfolio of brands and its partners You may receive these offers in advertising that is directed to you via third party sites and media platforms including in social media We may respond to your comments or questions or contact you if needed while processing a product or service you requested through our website We also may use the information you provide to contact you for your opinions on Kraft products services or websites As described in this Privacy Notice we also use the information we collect about you to improve our website products and services and to deliver content that is customized to your interests</evidence>
